; ======================
; Initial Chart of Accounts
; ======================

; Assets - Cash and liquidity
1970-01-01 open Assets:Cash:BRL BRL
1970-01-01 open Assets:Cash:USD USD
1970-01-01 open Assets:Bank:Checking:BRL BRL

; Assets - BR/US investments
1970-01-01 open Assets:Investments:BR:Brokerage BRL
1970-01-01 open Assets:Investments:BR:PETR4 PETR4
1970-01-01 open Assets:Investments:BR:IVVB11 IVVB11
1970-01-01 open Assets:Investments:US:Brokerage USD
1970-01-01 open Assets:Investments:US:AAPL AAPL

; Assets - Real estate (sub-accounting per asset)
1970-01-01 open Assets:RealEstate:Property1 BRL
1970-01-01 open Assets:RealEstate:Property1:CAPEX BRL

; Liabilities - Card and taxes
1970-01-01 open Liabilities:CreditCard:Nubank BRL
1970-01-01 open Liabilities:Taxes:Payable BRL

; Equity
1970-01-01 open Equity:OpeningBalances
1970-01-01 open Equity:Adjustments

; Income
1970-01-01 open Income:Salary BRL
1970-01-01 open Income:Investments:Dividends BRL
1970-01-01 open Income:RealEstate:Rent:Property1 BRL

; Expenses - General
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Food BRL
