1970-01-01 open Expenses:CreditCard:AnnualFee BRL
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Taxes BRL
; Conventions:
; - Accrual card accounting: expense at purchase time against Liabilities:CreditCard:*.
; - Cash accounting: settlement occurs when paying the statement (reduces cash and liability).
; - Real estate: OPEX in Expenses:Housing:* and CAPEX in Assets:RealEstate:*:CAPEX.
